            </li>
            <li>
                <i class="fas fa-spa fa-4x"></i>
                <h4>Theta Healing</h4>
                <p>A process of meditation that teaches people to develop natural intuition through changing their brain wave cycle to the more relaxed theta waves for the intention of exploring how emotional energy affects a persons health.</p>
            </li>
        </div>
    </ul>
